==== Mitochondrial Function

    - PBMC respirometry (Seahorse XF assay): basal respiration, maximal capacity, spare respiratory capacity, ATP-linked respiration
    - Plasma acylcarnitine profile
    - Lactate:pyruvate ratio
    - CoQ10 levels
    - Muscle biopsy (optional subset, n=20 per group): electron microscopy, respiratory chain enzyme activities, mtDNA copy number

